\begin_layout Theorem
Banach空间中的Picard定理.
 设
\begin_inset Formula $O\subseteq B$
\end_inset

 为Banach空间
\begin_inset Formula $B$
\end_inset

中的一个开子集, 设
\begin_inset Formula $F:O\to B$
\end_inset

为满足如下条件的映射:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Theorem
(i) 
\begin_inset Formula $F(X)$
\end_inset

将
\begin_inset Formula $O$
\end_inset

映入
\begin_inset Formula $B$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Theorem
(ii) 
\begin_inset Formula $F$
\end_inset

是局部Lipschitz连续的, 即, 对于任意的
\begin_inset Formula $X\in O$
\end_inset

, 存在
\begin_inset Formula $L>0$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

中的开邻域
\begin_inset Formula $U_{X}\subset O$
\end_inset

, 使得
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\norm{F(\widetilde{X})-F(\widehat{X})}_{B}\le L\norm{\widetilde{X}-\widehat{X}}_{B}\qquad\forall\widetilde{X},\widehat{X}\in U_{X}.
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Theorem
